{
  "stem": "3277.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was times that I was in terrible-- very terrible situations.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But, as I said, God was good to me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm alive.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I feel sorry that I am the only one [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] from the whole family.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't like to be in Poland, because some of those friends, they were-- I don't know whether to make career, or to be-- I was not on their side.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They treated me as an enemy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They couldn't do-- they couldn't put me into the jail.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But even-- even when I left Poland illegally, I used to get letters that the-- in the town where I used to live.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They treated-- they used to say that I am a hero.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If I could-- that Rosenthal, who was not such mentally so strong, and could do that job at that time, when most of those big shots in Poland were Russians, like the-- secretary of the-- the secretary of the war-- the war secretary-- Rokossovsky.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That at that time, that I could leave Poland illegally, that I am a hero.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And all the time, people were talking constantly-- of course, very-- [NON-ENGLISH] used to have trust, or they used to talk about me that-- how could I-- how could I leave Poland at that time, when the border was completely with all electronics-- how did he get out?",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Is there anything you did that you were ashamed of?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If I would have to do it again?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I am not ashamed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The other way.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I used to say to them, listen, I said a little bit, which is-- I said, I didn't-- my parents were very poor.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was not a capitalist.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
